  "FAQ": {
    "headline": "Questions, answered.",
    "q1": "Do my clients need to create an account?",
    "a1": "No. Your clients receive a unique, secure link to their project timeline. They can access it anytime without having to remember another password.",
    "q2": "Which tools does Progressly integrate with?",
    "a2": "We currently support GitHub, GitLab, Vercel, Netlify and OpenAI. We're constantly adding new integrations based on user feedback.",
    "q3": "Can I white-label the client view?",
    "a3": "Yes, our Agency plan allows you to remove Progressly branding, use your own logo, and host the timeline on your own custom domain.",
    "q4": "Is my project data secure?",
    "a4": "Absolutely. We only store the metadata needed to generate updates. Your actual code and design files never leave their original platforms.",
    "q5": "Can I cancel anytime?",
    "a5": "Yes, you can cancel your subscription at any time with a single click from your dashboard. No hidden fees or long-term contracts."
  },
